steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Add Post Build Action' from dropdown menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Aggregate Downstream Test Results link is displayed
Get Aggregate Downstream Test Results text in Post-build Actions
Get Aggregate Downstream Test Results link text
Clear Data for Jenkins instance http://localhost:8081/
